text:
Nice~! Madoka, you're doing great, great! Now,
direct your gaze over here... and give us a little smile...!

(Madoka doesn't necessarily
want to become an idol, right?)

(Was it really the right decision?
...To push her onto the path of being an idol...)
(No, let's stop. Let's keep believing in our instincts.)

Oh, by the way, what was the name of the unit again?
I think it was, Chill... Chill Chill...
